<plot>Raj Dixit lives with his younger brother, Rahul, who is disabled, both mentally and physically, from birth. Raj is also employed full-time, and after work, has the responsiblity of looking after Rahul, which leaves him no time for himself. His beautiful neighbor, Suman Gupta, is attracted to him, but Raj regards her as a friend only. When Mr. Khanna introduces him to his niece, Madhuri, both instantly falls in love. She meets with Rahul, and gets friendly with him. The only problem is that Madhuri will only marry Raj, if Rahul is institutionalized. Raj choses to get his Rahul admitted in a facility, much to delight of Madhuri, and together they start to plan their marriage, not realizing that things are going to take a turn for the worse.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?535669</url></doc>
